workspace 7 output HDMI-A-0 DisplayPort-0
workspace 8 output HDMI-A-0 DisplayPort-0
workspace 9 output HDMI-A-0 DisplayPort-0
workspace 10 output HDMI-A-0 DisplayPort-0
workspace 11 output eDP
